arts.ttl: Birmingham vs Millwall predictions: Lions can deny Blues a home win
arts.sum: Birmingham boosted their confidence after a tricky start to life in the Championship with a 4-0 win over Portsmouth last time out, but Phil Agius thinks Millwall could bring them back down to earth at St Andrew's.
